<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Erişim Reddedildi</title>
    <!-- DÜZELTME: CSS yolu /style.css olarak güncellendi -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css" />
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: var(--bg-primary); /* style.css değişkenleri kullanıldı */
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            padding: 60px 40px;
            background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        h1 {
            color: var(--red);
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .logout-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color), var(--accent-purple));
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .logout-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i> Erişim Reddedildi</h1>
        <p>Bu panele erişim yetkiniz bulunmamaktadır.</p>
        <p>Bu alan sadece bot sahibi ve yetkili kullanıcılar içindir.</p>
        <a href="/auth/logout" class="logout-btn"><i class="fa-solid fa-right-from-bracket"></i> Çıkış Yap</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
